This paper deals with text attribute transfer using neural networks, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes improvements to the existing methods, which involves training the neural network more efficiently, and this could fall under the sub-categories of cs.LG (Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper uses two datasets, which could suggest the involvement of computer vision (cs.CV) or neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories.
